{
  "title": "解决Centos\\Ubuntu is not in the sudoers file",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"position: relative;\"><embed id=\"xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd\" type=\"application/thunder_download_plugin\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">权限问题不仅在Windows下会出现问题，流行的Linux下也会有各种问题，如Ubuntu、Centos等。今天就来扯扯关于终端输入sudo后出现xx is not in the &nbsp;sudoers file.的提示。（</span><strong style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">xx代表你安装机器时的自定义用户名</strong><span style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">）</span><div alog-group=\"exp-content\" class=\"exp-content format-exp\" id=\"format-exp\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\"><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px;\"><div class=\"exp-content-body exp-brief-step\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><div class=\"exp-content-listblock\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div class=\"content-listblock-media\"><div class=\"content-listblock-image clearfix exp-image-center\" style=\"zoom: 1; padding-left: 340px; float: left; text-align: center;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/3ea51489ceccd652e61bba22.html?picindex=1\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left; margin-left: -250px;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"解决Centos\\Ubuntu is not in the sudoers file\" src=\"quiver-image-url/AB7D926504E7BAE5B049E7A39E6580B7.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"385\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div><div class=\"exp-brief-clear\" style=\"clear: both; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></div><div class=\"content-listblock-image clearfix exp-image-center\" style=\"zoom: 1; padding-left: 340px; float: left; text-align: center;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/3ea51489ceccd652e61bba22.html?picindex=2\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left; margin-left: -250px;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"解决Centos\\Ubuntu is not in the sudoers file\" src=\"quiver-image-url/9410463474F159FD2994B6B1696A18A5.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"410\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div><div class=\"exp-brief-clear\" style=\"clear: both; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px;\"><h2 class=\"exp-content-head\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 214, 216);\"><a name=\"section-2\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 100, 179);\"></a>工具/原料</h2><div class=\"exp-content-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><ul class=\"exp-content-unorderlist \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both;\"><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/unsortlist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><div class=\"content-list-text\">Linux系统终端</div></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px;\"><h2 class=\"exp-content-head\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 214, 216);\"><a name=\"section-3\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 100, 179);\"></a>方法/步骤</h2><div class=\"exp-content-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><ol class=\"exp-conent-orderlist\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both;\"><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-1\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 0px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">输入“su -”进入超级用户模式，输入装机时第一个设置的root密码，即可进入超级用户模式，如图3；</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/3ea51489ceccd652e61bba22.html?picindex=3\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"解决Centos\\Ubuntu is not in the sudoers file\" src=\"quiver-image-url/D3C7B54EF41C286D4D598BAB40E831C1.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"409\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-2\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">给sudoers文件加写入权限，输入“chmod u+w /etc/sudoers”，然后编辑sudoers文件，输入“gedit /etc/sudoers”，这时会弹出一个文本文件，如图4；</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/3ea51489ceccd652e61bba22.html?picindex=4\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"解决Centos\\Ubuntu is not in the sudoers file\" src=\"quiver-image-url/355E5E6401477A31BE67370EA0688AC8.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"413\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-3\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">在弹出的文本文件里找到 Allow root to ruan any commands anywhere这一行，如图5；</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/3ea51489ceccd652e61bba22.html?picindex=5\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"解决Centos\\Ubuntu is not in the sudoers file\" src=\"quiver-image-url/AE0514A5822E802549416CCFBF5A319F.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"411\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-4\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">在root &nbsp;ALL=(ALL) &nbsp;ALL 下面另起一行，输入“xx ALL=(ALL) &nbsp;ALL”(xx表示你的用户名)，然后保存退出，如图6；</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/3ea51489ceccd652e61bba22.html?picindex=6\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"解决Centos\\Ubuntu is not in the sudoers file\" src=\"quiver-image-url/EC50A9C6A09D9BB8EB51E7F4D2BE4FE7.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"500\" height=\"411\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-5\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">去掉sudoers文件的写入权限，如图7；（这一步主要为了安全，随手养成好习惯，自己玩的虚拟机可以不做，如果是服务器什么等联外网的，切记切记。）再输入获取管理权限的sudo就正常了，不会再提示xx is not in the &nbsp;sudoers file.的问题了</p></div><div class=\"last-item\" style=\"position: relative; height: 13px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span class=\"last-item-end\" style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 13px; position: absolute; bottom: 0px; left: -48px; display: block;\">END</span></div></li></ol></div></div><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px;\"><h2 class=\"exp-content-head\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 214, 216);\"><a name=\"section-4\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 100, 179);\"></a>注意事项</h2><div class=\"exp-content-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><ul class=\"exp-content-unorderlist \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both;\"><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/unsortlist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><div class=\"content-list-text\">终端输入大小写空格</div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/unsortlist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><div class=\"content-list-text\">“su -”命令以及良好操作的习惯</div></li></ul></div></div><div id=\"auto-app-placehold\"></div><div class=\"prompt\" style=\"position: relative; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); padding: 18px 0px 18px 20px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); margin-top: 40px;\"><span class=\"prompt-ico\" style=\"background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/article/article-sprite-v1.png); width: 18px; height: 18px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 10px; background-position: -241px -312px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></span></div></div><div style=\"clear: both;\"></div></div>"
    }
  ]
}